    "abstract": "<jats:title>ABSTRACT</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>This large nationwide population-based seroepidemiological study provides evidence on the effectiveness of physical distancing (&gt;1.5m) and indoor group size reductions on SARS-CoV-2 infection. Additionally, young adults seem to play a significant role in viral spread, opposed to children up until the primary school age with whom close contact is permitted.</jats:p>",
